<div class='communityQuestionAndAnswer'>
<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/1542376-i-have-a-huge-question-can-anyone-answer">I have a huge question. Can anyone answer me who is the POV or the characters described in one scene of the Epilogue??
It goes this way:`Tales have many strands, smaller, larger. An incidental...The letter was discarded, tumbling in dust and wind, and disappearing.`

Is it the letter Spring Rain sent to Tai?
I found Rain and Tai to be the most fascinating and heartbreaking characters of the novel. I formed tears.</a>
</div>
